# 📖 Day 7 – GROUP BY & HAVING

## Topics Covered

- GROUP BY
- HAVING

GROUP BY groups rows before applying aggregate functions.

```sql
SELECT department,
AVG(salary)
FROM Employee
GROUP BY department;
```

HAVING filters groups.

```sql
SELECT department,
AVG(salary)
FROM Employee
GROUP BY department
HAVING AVG(salary)>50000;
```

### Difference

| WHERE | HAVING |
|--------|---------|
| Filters rows | Filters groups |

